        "created_at": "2023-03-06T07:16:16.068Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Glad you enjoyed it Chris.</p>\n<p>We punched in a bottle of 2019 Domaine Bruno Lorenzon Montagny 1er Cru \u2018Le Mont Laurent\u2019 last night. It is starting to drink really well. Bruno is such a perfectionist and it is great to see him get some recognition for all of his hard work.</p>",
